Valentine Diefenthaler, Respondent v. The Metropolitan Elevated Railway Company, et al., Appellants. Decided January 11, 1892. Appeaf by defendants from judgment entered upon the report of a referee. Davies & Rapallo, for appellants. Edwin M. Felt, for respondent.

Before Freedman, P. J., McAdam and Gildersleeve, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Judgment affirmed, with costs.
